    "attributes": {
        "action": "Provide more funding for school repairs",
        "additional_details": "All children have the right to learn in a safe, warm environment. For some children school is their own safe place. The Government must pay attention to its duty of care and protect young children from the dangers that they currently face within situations of disrepair.",
        "background": "Many schools are facing increasing repair concerns, causing safety issues. I would like the government to provide more funding for school repairs, allowing them to complete minor and major works. The funding should also be used for regular safety inspections.",
